    {
      "index": 2,
      "title": "Foundations of Blockchain Architecture",
      "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      background-color: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;\n      padding: clamp(2rem, 5vh, 5rem);\n      gap: 2rem;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .slide-header {\n      text-align: left;\n    }\n\n    .slide-header h1 {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin: 0;\n      text-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--accent-glow);\n    }\n\n    .slide-content {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n      gap: 2rem;\n      align-items: start;\n    }\n\n    .concept-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 1rem;\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      position: relative;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    .concept-card:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      transform: translateY(-5px);\n    }\n\n    .concept-card h2 {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin-top: 0;\n    }\n\n    .concept-card p {\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n    }\n\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n\n    @keyframes fadeInUp {\n      to {\n        opacity: 1;\n        transform: translateY(0);\n      }\n    }\n\n    .tag {\n      display: inline-block;\n      font-size: 0.7rem;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 1px;\n      background: var(--accent-glow);\n      color: var(--text);\n      padding: 2px 8px;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.1s\">Foundations of Blockchain Architecture</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-content\">\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.3s\">\n      <span class=\"tag\">Data Integrity</span>\n      <h2>Immutable Ledgers</h2>\n      <p>Cryptographic hashing ensures that once data is written to a block, it cannot be altered without changing every subsequent block. This creates a verifiable, permanent history of transactions.</p>\n      <p><strong>Core:</strong> SHA-256 • Merkle Trees • Chain-of-Trust</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.5s\">\n      <span class=\"tag\">Network Layer</span>\n      <h2>P2P Networking</h2>\n      <p>Distributed nodes maintain the ledger without a central authority. Gossiping protocols ensure state synchronization across the globe with high fault tolerance.</p>\n      <p><strong>Core:</strong> Node Discovery • Gossip Protocols • Decentralization</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.7s\">\n      <span class=\"tag\">Consensus Evolution</span>\n      <h2>The PoW to PoS Shift</h2>\n      <p>Moving from computationally expensive Proof-of-Work (mining) to Proof-of-Stake (validators) drastically reduces the carbon footprint and energy requirements.</p>\n      <p><strong>Impact:</strong> &gt;99% energy reduction • Higher Scalability • Sustainable Growth</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
      "snapshot_b64": null,
      "snapshot_url": null,
      "audit": null,
      "approved": true,
      "status": "draft",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "title": "Smart Contract Logic and Execution",
      "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;\n      gap: 2rem;\n      padding: 2rem;\n      height: calc(100% - 80px);\n      align-items: center;\n    }\n    .slide-header {\n      padding: 2rem 2rem 0 2rem;\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n    }\n    .slide-title {\n      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);\n      color: var(--text);\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    .code-container {\n      background: var(--code-bg);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 1rem;\n      position: relative;\n      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n    }\n    .code-container pre {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: 'Cascadia Code', 'Fira Code', monospace;\n      font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.2vw, 1.1rem);\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n    .content-list {\n      list-style: none;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n    .content-item {\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n      padding-left: 1.5rem;\n      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .content-item:hover {\n      transform: translateX(10px);\n    }\n    .item-title {\n      font-weight: bold;\n      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      display: block;\n      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\n    }\n    .item-desc {\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n    }\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: revealIn 0.6s forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n    @keyframes revealIn {\n      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n    }\n    .highlight-line {\n      background: rgba(var(--accent-glow), 0.2);\n      display: block;\n      width: 100%;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"slide-title\">Smart Contract Logic and Execution</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-grid\">\n    <div class=\"code-container reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.2s\">\n      <pre class=\"language-solidity\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-solidity\">\ncontract Vault {\n    // State management: Storage costs Gas\n    mapping(address =&gt; uint256) public balances;\n\n    function deposit() external payable {\n        // Deterministic logic: No random API calls\n        require(msg.value &gt; 0, \"Must send ETH\");\n        \n        // Gas optimization: Local cache of state\n        uint256 currentBal = balances[msg.sender];\n        balances[msg.sender] = currentBal + msg.value;\n    }\n\n    function withdraw(uint256 _amount) external {\n        // Security: Check-Effects-Interactions pattern\n        require(balances[msg.sender] &gt;= _amount, \"Insufficient\");\n        \n        balances[msg.sender] -= _amount;\n        payable(msg.sender).transfer(_amount);\n    }\n}\n      </code></pre>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-area\">\n      <ul class=\"content-list\">\n        <li class=\"content-item reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.4s\">\n          <span class=\"item-title\">Deterministic Execution</span>\n          <span class=\"item-desc\">Contracts must behave identically across all nodes. No external API calls; all data must be on-chain.</span>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"content-item reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.6s\">\n          <span class=\"item-title\">Solidity &amp; Rust</span>\n          <span class=\"item-desc\">Industry standards for trust: Solidity (EVM) and Rust (Solana/Polkadot) focus on memory safety and strict typing.</span>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"content-item reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.8s\">\n          <span class=\"item-title\">Gas &amp; State Optimization</span>\n          <span class=\"item-desc\">Every state change costs \"Gas\". Optimizing storage slots is critical for scalability and cost-reduction.</span>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"content-item reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 1.0s\">\n          <span class=\"item-title\">Security Auditing</span>\n          <span class=\"item-desc\">Preventing re-entrancy and integer overflows through formal verification and rigorous peer review.</span>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
      "snapshot_b64": null,
      "snapshot_url": null,
      "audit": null,
      "approved": true,
      "status": "draft",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "title": "Solving the Scalability Trilemma",
      "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body); padding: 2rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 2rem;\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin-top: 2rem;\n    }\n    .slide-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--text);\n      text-align: center;\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n    .comparison-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 1rem;\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .card-header {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);\n      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n    }\n    .point-list {\n      list-style: none;\n      padding: 0;\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    .point-item {\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem);\n      line-height: 1.5;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n      gap: 0.5rem;\n    }\n    .point-item strong {\n      color: var(--text);\n      display: block;\n    }\n    .trilemma-footer {\n      margin-top: 3rem;\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 1rem;\n      background: var(--code-bg);\n      border-radius: 0.5rem;\n      font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      border: 1px dashed var(--border);\n      max-width: 800px;\n      margin-left: auto;\n      margin-right: auto;\n    }\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: revealIn 0.6s forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n    @keyframes revealIn {\n      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n    }\n    .badge {\n      font-size: 0.7rem;\n      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      background: var(--accent);\n      color: var(--bg);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      font-weight: bold;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <h1 class=\"slide-title reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0s\">Solving the Scalability Trilemma</h1>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-grid\">\n    <!-- Left Column: Modular & Layered -->\n    <div class=\"comparison-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.2s\">\n      <div class=\"card-header\">\n        <span>Modular Approach</span>\n        <span class=\"badge\">Decentralized</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"point-list\">\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>Ethereum &amp; Layer 2s</strong>\n            Offloads execution to Rollups (Optimism, Arbitrum) while retaining L1 security.\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>Polkadot Parachains</strong>\n            Native interoperability via a Relay Chain, allowing specialized shards to scale independently.\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>The Trade-off</strong>\n            Prioritizes <em>Security &amp; Decentralization</em>; accepts slight complexity in user experience (bridging).\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Right Column: Monolithic & Integrated -->\n    <div class=\"comparison-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.4s\">\n      <div class=\"card-header\">\n        <span>Monolithic Approach</span>\n        <span class=\"badge\">High Speed</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"point-list\">\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>Solana's Architecture</strong>\n            Single-state machine with Proof-of-History for massive throughput and sub-second finality.\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>Layer 1 Scaling</strong>\n            Vertical scaling through high-spec hardware and optimized parallel execution (Sealevel).\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>The Trade-off</strong>\n            Prioritizes <em>Speed &amp; Performance</em>; faces challenges in hardware accessibility for validators.\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"trilemma-footer reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.6s\">\n    <strong>The Trilemma:</strong> Security ⬌ Speed ⬌ Decentralization. <br>\n    No single architecture solves all three perfectly; solutions are selected based on the specific use-case requirements.\n  </div>\n</section>",
      "snapshot_b64": null,
      "snapshot_url": null,
      "audit": null,
      "approved": true,
      "status": "draft",
      "metadata": {}
